      "type": "concept_card",
      "title": "Fact Family Triangle",
      "content": "A fact family uses 3 numbers to make 4 equations. For 4, 7, and 28: 4 × 7 = 28, 7 × 4 = 28, 28 ÷ 4 = 7, 28 ÷ 7 = 4. All four facts live in the same family!",
      "cpa_phase": "pictorial",
      "visual_type": "diagram",
